<template>
  <Card class="border">
    <template #title>All Daily Targets Reached (%)</template>
    <template #content>
      <Knob v-model="value" />
    </template>
  </Card>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      value: 70
    };
  },
};
</script>

<style scoped>
.border {
  border-top: 4px solid var(--pink);
}
</style>
